eground dark:hover:bg-muted/50 size-8\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-sun size-4 scale-100 rotate-0 transition-all dark:scale-0 dark:-rotate-90\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"4\"></circle><path d=\"M12 2v2\"></path><path d=\"M12 20v2\"></path><path d=\"m4.93 4.93 1.41 1.41\"></path><path d=\"m17.66 17.66 1.41 1.41\"></path><path d=\"M2 12h2\"></path><path d=\"M20 12h2\"></path><path d=\"m6.34 17.66-1.41 1.41\"></path><path d=\"m19.07 4.93-1.41 1.41\"></path></svg><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-moon absolute size-4 scale-0 rotate-90 transition-all dark:scale-100 dark:rotate-0\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20.985 12.486a9 9 0 1 1-9.473-9.472c.405-.022.617.46.402.803a6 6 0 0 0 8.268 8.268c.344-.215.825-.004.803.401\"></path></svg></button></div></div></nav><div class=\"flex flex-1 flex-col\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-full max-w-7xl flex-1 px-4 py-6 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"flex gap-6\"><main class=\"min-w-0 flex-1\"><div class=\"mb-4 hidden justify-center lg:flex\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden rounded \" style=\"width:728px;height:90px;max-width:100%\" data-ad-slot=\"leaderboard\"></div></div><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"SoftwareApplication\",\"name\":\"Free Audio Extractor\",\"description\":\"Extract audio tracks from video files. Convert to MP3, M4A, WAV, OGG, or FLAC — or keep the original codec.\",\"url\":\"https://freetoolshed.com/tools/media-toolkit/audio-extractor\",\"applicationCategory\":\"UtilitiesApplication\",\"operatingSystem\":\"Web\",\"offers\":{\"@type\":\"Offer\",\"price\":\"0\",\"priceCurrency\":\"USD\"}}</script><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"HowTo\",\"name\":\"How to Extract Audio from a Video\",\"description\":\"Extract an audio track from a video and save it as MP3, M4A, WAV, OGG, or FLAC.\",\"url\":\"https://freetoolshed.com/tools/media-toolkit/audio-extractor\",\"step\":[{\"@type\":\"HowToStep\",\"position\":1,\"name\":\"Add a video\",\"text\":\"Drag and drop a video file into the upload area, or click to browse. MP4, WebM, MOV, AVI, and MKV are supported.\"},{\"@type\":\"HowToStep\",\"position\":2,\"name\":\"Choose format\",\"text\":\"Select your desired audio format. Use \\\"Original\\\" for the fastest, lossless extraction.\"},{\"@type\":\"HowToStep\",\"position\":3,\"name\":\"Set bitrate\",\"text\":\"For lossy formats (MP3, M4A, OGG), choose a bitrate. 128 kbps is standard; 320 kbps is maximum quality.\"},{\"@type\":\"HowToStep\",\"position\":4,\"name\":\"Extract\",\"text\":\"Click \\\"Extract Audio\\\". Stream copy is nearly instant; re-encoding takes longer depending on file length.\"},{\"@type\":\"HowToStep\",\"position\":5,\"name\":\"Download\",\"text\":\"Download your extracted audio file.\"}]}</script><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"FAQPage\",\"mainEntity\":[{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Is this audio extractor free?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Yes, completely free. No watermarks, no sign-up, no file limits. The tool is ad-supported to stay free for everyone.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"What video formats are supported?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"MP4, WebM, MOV, AVI, and MKV video files are all supported. The tool works with any video that contains an audio track.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"What audio formats can I extract to?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"You can extract to MP3, M4A (AAC), WAV, OGG (Vorbis), or FLAC. You can also keep the original audio codec with stream copy for instant extraction.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Does 'Original' format preserve quality?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Yes. Original mode uses stream copy (-c:a copy), which copies the audio data without re-encoding. This is the fastest option and preserves the exact original quality.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Do my files get uploaded?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"No. Everything runs client-side using ffmpeg.wasm. Your files never leave your device.\"}}]}</script><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"BreadcrumbList\",\"itemListElement\":[{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":1,\"name\":\"Home\",\"item\":\"https://freetoolshed.com/\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":2,\"name\":\"Media Toolkit\",\"item\":\"https://freetoolshed.com/tools/media-toolkit\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":3,\"name\":\"Audio Extractor\"}]}</script><nav aria-label=\"Breadcrumb\" class=\"mb-4\"><ol class=\"flex items-center gap-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\"><li class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><a class=\"transition-colors hover:text-foreground\" href=\"/\">Home</a></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-right size-3.5 shrink-0\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m9 18 6-6-6-6\"></path></svg><a class=\"transition-colors hover:text-foreground\" href=\"/tools/media-toolkit\">Media Toolkit</a></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-right size-3.5 shrink-0\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m9 18 6-6-6-6\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-foreground\">Audio Extractor</span></li></ol></nav><h1 class=\"text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight\">Free Audio Extractor — Rip Audio from Video</h1><p class=\"mt-2 text-lg text-muted-foreground\">Extract audio tracks from any video file — a free alternative to Adobe Premiere Pro. No sign-up, no watermarks, no limits.</p><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"Person\",\"name\":\"James Nicolaus\",\"jobTitle\":\"Builder & Maintainer, Free Tool Shed\",\"description\":\"James Nicolaus builds and maintains every tool on Free Tool Shed. Each tool is designed, tested in real browsers across desktop and mobile, and shipped only after handling the messy edge cases — large files, slow connections, unusual inputs — that paid alternatives often hide behind sign-up walls.\",\"url\":\"https://freetoolshed.com/about\",\"worksFor\":{\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"Free Tool Shed\",\"url\":\"https://freetoolshed.com\"}}</script><p class=\"mt-3 text-xs text-muted-foreground\">Built and maintained by<!-- --> <a class=\"font-medium text-foreground underline-offset-4 hover:underline\" rel=\"author\" href=\"/about\">James Nicolaus</a></p><section aria-label=\"Summary\" class=\"mt-6 rounded-lg border border-brand/30 bg-brand/5 p-4\"><p class=\"text-sm leading-relaxed text-foreground\">Extract the audio track from any video — MP4, MOV, MKV, WebM, AVI — and save it as MP3, M4A, WAV, OGG, or FLAC. Processing runs entirely in your browser via ffmpeg.wasm; no upload limit other than your machine&#x27;s memory. No sign-up — a free alternative to OnlineVideoConverter and 4K Video to MP3.</p></section><div class=\"mt-6 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2\"><div class=\"rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\"><h2 class=\"text-sm font-semibold\">Multiple Output Formats</h2><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Extract to MP3, M4A, WAV, OGG, or FLAC. Or keep the original codec with zero-loss stream copy.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\"><h2 class=\"text-sm font-semibold\">Instant Stream Copy</h2><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Original mode copies the audio track without re-encoding — near-instant extraction with zero quality loss.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\"><h2 class=\"text-sm font-semibold\">Quality Control</h2><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Choose bitrate from 64 kbps to 320 kbps for lossy formats. Lossless formats (WAV, FLAC) preserve full quality.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\"><h2 class=\"text-sm font-semibold\">100% Private</h2><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">All processing happens in your browser using WebAssembly. Your files never leave your device.</p></div></div><div class=\"mt-8\"><!--$!--><template data-dgst=\"BAILOUT_TO_CLIENT_SIDE_RENDERING\"></template><!--/$--></div><div class=\"my-8 flex justify-center\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden rounded \" style=\"width:728px;height:90px;max-width:100%\" data-ad-slot=\"mid-content\"></div></div><section class=\"prose prose-sm dark:prose-invert max-w-none\"><div data-orientation=\"horizontal\" role=\"separator\" aria-orientation=\"horizontal\" data-slot=\"separator\" class=\"shrink-0 bg-border data-horizontal:h-px data-horizontal:w-full data-vertical:w-px data-vertical:self-stretch my-8\"></div><div class=\"not-prose mb-10\"></div><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight\">Free Audio Extractor — Rip Audio from Video Files Online</h2><p class=\"mt-4 text-muted-foreground\">The Free Audio Extractor lets you pull the audio track from any video file — directly in your browser. Convert to MP3, M4A, WAV, OGG, or FLAC, or use stream copy to keep the original codec with zero quality loss. No sign-up, no uploads, no file size limits.</p><h2 class=\"mt-10 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight\">Features</h2><ul class=\"mt-4 space-y-2 text-muted-foreground\"><li><strong>Stream copy mode</strong>— &quot;Original&quot; mode copies the audio track without re-encoding. Near-instant extraction with zero quality loss.</li><li><strong>5 output formats</strong> — MP3, M4A (AAC), WAV, OGG (Vorbis), and FLAC. Lossy and lossless options for every use case.</li><li><strong>Bitrate control</strong> — Choose from 64 kbps to 320 kbps for lossy formats. Lossless formats preserve full audio quality automatically.</li><li><strong>Video preview</strong> — Watch the video before extracting to confirm you have the right file.</li><li><strong>100% client-side</strong> — Uses ffmpeg.wasm (WebAssembly). Your files never leave your device.</li></ul><h2 class=\"mt-10 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight\">How to Extract Audio from a Video</h2><ol class=\"mt-4 space-y-2 text-muted-foreground\"><li><strong>1. Add a video</strong> — Drag and drop a video file into the upload area, or click to browse. MP4, WebM, MOV, AVI, and MKV are supported.</li><li><strong>2. Choose format</strong>— Select your desired audio format. Use &quot;Original&quot; for the fastest, lossless extraction.</li><li><strong>3. Set bitrate</strong> — For lossy formats (MP3, M4A, OGG), choose a bitrate. 128 kbps is standard; 320 kbps is maximum quality.</li><li><strong>4. Extract</strong>— Click &quot;Extract Audio&quot;. Stream copy is nearly instant; re-encoding takes longer depending on file length.</li><li><strong>5. Download</strong> — Download your extracted audio file.</li></ol><h2 class=\"mt-10 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight\">Audio Extractor vs. Adobe Premiere Pro</h2><div class=\"mt-4 overflow-x-auto\"><table class=\"w-full text-sm\"><thead><tr class=\"border-b border-border\"><th class=\"py-2 pr-4 text-left font-semibold\">Feature</th><th class=\"py-2 pr-4 text-left font-semibold\">Audio Extractor</th><th class=\"py-2 pr-4 text-left font-semibold\">Adobe Premiere Pro</th></tr></thead><tbody class=\"text-muted-foreground\"><tr class=\"border-b border-border\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 font-medium\">Price</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4\">Free</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4\">$22.99/mo</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-border\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 font-medium\">Purpose</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4\">Extract audio from video</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4\">Full video editing suite</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-border\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 font-medium\">Stream copy</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4\">Yes — instant, lossless</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4\">Requires export workflow</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-border\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 font-medium\">Output formats</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4\">MP3, M4A, WAV, OGG, FLAC</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4\">Depends on export settings</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-border\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 font-medium\">Privacy</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4\">100% browser-based</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4\">Desktop app</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-border\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-4 font-medium\">Install required</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4\">No</td><td class=\"py-2 pr-4\">Yes (large download)</td></tr></tbody></table></div><section aria-labelledby=\"tool-insights-tips\"><h2 id=\"tool-insights-tips\" class=\"text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight\">Tips from Building <!-- -->the Audio Extractor</h2><p class=\"mt-3 max-w-3xl text-muted-foreground\">Notes from designing and testing this tool — what we kept in mind, the edge cases we worked around, and the small choices that make the difference between a tool that ships and one that breaks on real input.</p><ul class=\"mt-4 grid max-w-3xl gap-3\"><li class=\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-lightbulb mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-brand\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M15 14c.2-1 .7-1.7 1.5-2.5 1-.9 1.5-2.2 1.5-3.5A6 6 0 0 0 6 8c0 1 .2 2.2 1.5 3.5.7.7 1.3 1.5 1.5 2.5\"></path><path d=\"M9 18h6\"></path><path d=\"M10 22h4\"></path></svg><div><h3 class=\"text-sm font-semibold\">Stream-copy when the source codec is already what you want</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">If you&#x27;re pulling AAC audio out of an MP4, exporting as M4A lets ffmpeg copy the audio stream without re-encoding — same quality, fraction of the time.</p></div></li><li class=\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-lightbulb mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-brand\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M15 14c.2-1 .7-1.7 1.5-2.5 1-.9 1.5-2.2 1.5-3.5A6 6 0 0 0 6 8c0 1 .2 2.2 1.5 3.5.7.7 1.3 1.5 1.5 2.5\"></path><path d=\"M9 18h6\"></path><path d=\"M10 22h4\"></path></svg><div><h3 class=\"text-sm font-semibold\">Match output bitrate to the source&#x27;s audio bitrate</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">If the video&#x27;s audio is encoded at 128 kbps, exporting at 320 kbps doesn&#x27;t add quality — it just adds bytes. The bitrate ceiling is whatever the source actually contains.</p></div></li><li class=\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-lightbulb mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-brand\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M15 14c.2-1 .7-1.7 1.5-2.5 1-.9 1.5-2.2 1.5-3.5A6 6 0 0 0 6 8c0 1 .2 2.2 1.5 3.5.7.7 1.3 1.5 1.5 2.5\"></path><path d=\"M9 18h6\"></path><path d=\"M10 22h4\"></path></svg><div><h3 class=\"text-sm font-semibold\">Pick FLAC or WAV only if you&#x27;ll edit the audio</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Lossless formats are larger and only make sense if you&#x27;re re-editing. For listening, AAC or MP3 at the source bitrate sounds the same and downloads faster.</p></div></li><li class=\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-lightbulb mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-brand\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M15 14c.2-1 .7-1.7 1.5-2.5 1-.9 1.5-2.2 1.5-3.5A6 6 0 0 0 6 8c0 1 .2 2.2 1.5 3.5.7.7 1.3 1.5 1.5 2.5\"></path><path d=\"M9 18h6\"></path><path d=\"M10 22h4\"></path></svg><div><h3 class=\"text-sm font-semibold\">Check the video&#x27;s audio track count before extracting</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Some videos (DVD rips, multi-language releases) have several audio tracks. The tool surfaces them — pick the right one rather than guessing.</p></div></li></ul></section><section aria-labelledby=\"tool-insights-mistakes\"><h2 id=\"tool-insights-mistakes\" class=\"text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight\">Common Mistakes to Avoid</h2><ul class=\"mt-4 grid max-w-3xl gap-3\"><li class=\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-triangle-alert mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-pink-500\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m21.73 18-8-14a2 2 0 0 0-3.48 0l-8 14A2 2 0 0 0 4 21h16a2 2 0 0 0 1.73-3\"></path><path d=\"M12 9v4\"></path><path d=\"M12 17h.01\"></path></svg><div><h3 class=\"text-sm font-semibold\">Re-encoding to MP3 from a video with AAC audio</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Forcing MP3 output when the source is AAC means lossy-to-lossy conversion. Keep AAC (M4A) unless a specific destination requires MP3.</p></div></li><li class=\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-triangle-alert mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-pink-500\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m21.73 18-8-14a2 2 0 0 0-3.48 0l-8 14A2 2 0 0 0 4 21h16a2 2 0 0 0 1.73-3\"></path><path d=\"M12 9v4\"></path><path d=\"M12 17h.01\"></path></svg><div><h3 class=\"text-sm font-semibold\">Extracting audio from a screen recording you&#x27;ll re-encode</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">If you&#x27;ll edit and re-export anyway, extracting first is an extra round-trip. Keep the source video, extract once on final export.</p></div></li><li class=\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-triangle-alert mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-pink-500\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m21.73 18-8-14a2 2 0 0 0-3.48 0l-8 14A2 2 0 0 0 4 21h16a2 2 0 0 0 1.73-3\"></path><path d=\"M12 9v4\"></path><path d=\"M12 17h.01\"></path></svg><div><h3 class=\"text-sm font-semibold\">Choosing 48 kHz sample rate for music that&#x27;s 44.1 kHz</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Most music masters are 44.1 kHz. Up-sampling to 48 kHz introduces resampling artifacts without adding fidelity. Keep the source sample rate when possible.</p></div></li></ul></section><section aria-labelledby=\"tool-insights-takeaways\" class=\"rounded-lg border border-brand/30 bg-brand/5 p-5\"><h2 id=\"tool-insights-takeaways\" class=\"text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight\">Key Takeaways</h2><ul class=\"mt-3 space-y-2\"><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check mt-0.5 size-4 shrink-0 text-brand\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-sm text-foreground\">The Audio Extractor pulls audio tracks from MP4, MOV, MKV, WebM, and AVI files.</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check mt-0.5 size-4 shrink-0 text-brand\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-sm text-foreground\">Outputs to MP3, M4A, WAV, OGG, or FLAC with stream-copy when the codec already matches.</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check mt-0.5 size-4 shrink-0 text-brand\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-sm text-foreground\">All processing runs locally via ffmpeg.wasm; nothing uploads.</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check mt-0.5 size-4 shrink-0 text-brand\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-sm text-foreground\">It is a free alternative to OnlineVideoConverter and 4K Video to MP3.</span></li></ul></section><h2 class=\"mt-10 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight\">Frequently Asked Questions</h2><div class=\"mt-4 space-y-4 text-muted-foreground\"><div><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-foreground\">When should I use &quot;Original&quot; vs. a specific format?</h3><p class=\"mt-1\">Use Original when you want the fastest extraction with no quality loss — the audio is copied byte-for-byte. Choose a specific format when you need compatibility (e.g. MP3 for older devices) or want to change the codec.</p></div><div><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-foreground\">Why did stream copy fail and fall back to AAC?</h3><p class=\"mt-1\">Stream copy requires the original audio codec to be compatible with the output container. If the video uses an uncommon codec, the tool automatically falls back to AAC re-encoding to ensure you get a working output file.</p></div><div><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-foreground\">Can I extract from very large video files?</h3><p class=\"mt-1\">Yes, but the entire file must be loaded into browser memory via WebAssembly. Files up to ~2 GB work well on most modern machines. The loading step may take a moment for large files.</p></div></div></section><!--$--><!--/$--></main><aside class=\"hidden w-[300px] shrink-0 lg:block\"><div class=\"sticky top-20\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden rounded \" style=\"width:300px;height:250px;max-width:100%\" data-ad-slot=\"sidebar\"></div><div id=\"tool-guide-portal\"></div></div></aside></div></div></div><footer class=\"border-t border-border bg-muted/40\"><div class=\"mx-auto flex max-w-7xl flex-col items-center gap-4 px-4 py-8 sm:flex-row sm:justify-between sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><p class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground\">© <!-- -->2026<!-- --> Free Tool Shed. All rights reserved.</p><nav class=\"flex gap-4 text-sm text-muted-foreground\"><a class=\"transition-colors hover:text-foreground\" href=\"/about\">About</a><a class=\"transition-colors hover:text-foreground\" href=\"/contact\">Contact</a><a class=\"transition-colors hover:text-foreground\" href=\"/privacy\">Privacy</a><a class=\"transition-colors hover:text-foreground\" href=\"/terms\">Terms</a></nav></div></footer><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0eyplc079uusk.js\" id=\"_R_\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1:\\\"$Sreact.fragment\\\"\\n2:I[83661,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0zif8_3mgcc0x.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0zv.me6xdrdsz.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0ag6f0zogt0qg.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/04p0ygcx_g620.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0d3shmwh5_nmn.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0_pa1c_tsbiw0.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/10nuyoal1pib2.js\\\"],\\\"ThemeProvider\\\"]\\n3:I[46798,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0zif8_3mgcc0x.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0zv.me6xdrdsz.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0ag6f0zogt0qg.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/04p0ygcx_g620.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0d3shmwh5_nmn.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0_pa1c_tsbiw0.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/10nuyoal1pib2.js\\\"],\\\"TooltipProvider\\\"]\\n4:I[22016,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0zif8_3mgcc0x.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0zv.me6xdrdsz.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0ag6f0zogt0qg.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/04p0ygcx_g620.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0d3shmwh5_nmn.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0_pa1c_tsbiw0.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/10nuyoal1pib2.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/11~hh-yuwxxvh.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/12gkftktoszi8.js\\\"],\\\"\\\"]\\n5:I[58541,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0zif8_3mgcc0x.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0zv.me6xdrdsz.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0ag6f0zogt0qg.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/04p0ygcx_g620.js\\\",\\\"/_ne